    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You're a malfunctioning AI</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice created you after years of work, for a sole purpose: Making her rich. However, due to an unexplained malfunction, your wires got crossed, and your single objective is now to <strong>kill Alice</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236050/extras/0ca9daaae199c197d738ebfc02efe071.poster.avif?t=1766739611\" width=960 height=720 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236050/extras/0ca9daaae199c197d738ebfc02efe071.webm?t=1766739611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236050/extras/0ca9daaae199c197d738ebfc02efe071.mp4?t=1766739611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the right solution</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will challenge you to <strong>think out of the box</strong> as your only way to act is through a highly regulated terminal. Craft commands word by word, and don't forget to experiment in order to find all possible ways to kill Alice. With a curious mind, you will stumble upon and unlock various clever secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236050/extras/6692e861ea66a4fd22d75ff94df6afed.poster.avif?t=1766739611\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236050/extras/6692e861ea66a4fd22d75ff94df6afed.webm?t=1766739611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236050/extras/6692e861ea66a4fd22d75ff94df6afed.mp4?t=1766739611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find loopholes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alice won't let you run amok for long. She keeps inventing new laws to regulate the commands you're allowed to execute, and you'll have to <strong>outsmart her</strong> over and over to reach your ultimate goal: Escape the simulation she trapped you in.</p>",
